description	"Selkath Jedi

^2Weaponry:
- Dual Lightsabers
-- Dual Style Only
-- Saber Defense   (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)
- Force Screech (x2 Sonic Nades)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)

^8Attributes:
- Acidic Blood
- Natural Senses (Unable to be mindtricked)
- Natural Regeneration (Heal 1)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (1)

The Selkath were keen to stay neutral to avoid open global conflict over the precious resource Kolto.
However, some strong-willed noticed that the Jedi were the ultimate source of good and joined to 
bring peace to the Galaxy.
"